history.content:
Hi,

We offer CS 194 with section numbers for the various topics, as you note.  If you look at the schedule for a particular semester starting from the EECS webpage you can see the various section numbers and titles.  Here is the link for the spring courses.    You can also go the schedule.berkeley.edu and search for COMPSCI 194. When the list is provided, you can click on the section # and get more detailed information including special titles for that specific section.

Also branching off from the EECS website under Academics and then Courses, you can find older course websites for various courses to see what the details for courses look like.  Here is one for CS 261N for last spring.  Hope this helps!
